please just have one friend.

00:03:34.350 --> 00:03:37.894 align:middle line:90%
And my dad was--

00:03:37.894 --> 00:03:42.610 align:middle line:84%
I've forgiven him everything,
but he was very abusive

00:03:42.610 --> 00:03:44.600 align:middle line:90%
physically and emotionally.

00:03:44.600 --> 00:03:45.400 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Yeah.

00:03:45.400 --> 00:03:48.520 align:middle line:84%
>> VALENTINE: You know,
when I got to this point,

00:03:48.520 --> 00:03:51.640 align:middle line:84%
a pivotal point for me was when
I got to my early 20s and it

00:03:51.640 --> 00:03:54.200 align:middle line:84%
