part Native American,

00:03:57.050 --> 00:04:00.130 align:middle line:84%
I sought out a Native
American counselor

00:04:00.130 --> 00:04:02.320 align:middle line:84%
to help me work through
the daddy stuff.

00:04:02.320 --> 00:04:04.480 align:middle line:84%
