day and said, you know,

00:04:04.480 --> 00:04:10.390 align:middle line:84%
your dad must have loved
you an incredible amount

00:04:10.390 --> 00:04:15.820 align:middle line:84%
in order to come to Earth and
inhabit that part in your life

00:04:15.820 --> 00:04:20.500 align:middle line:84%
and be such a bad person
so that you could turn out

00:04:20.500 --> 00:04:23.420 align:middle line:90%
to be such a wonderful person.

00:04:23.420 --> 00:04:25.250 align:middle line:84%
And to me, that was
instant healing.

00:04:25.250 --> 00:04:26.050 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Right.

00:04:26.050 --> 00:04:29.020 align:middle line:84%
>> VALENTINE: But it also
sort of set the stage for me,

00:04:29.020 --> 00:04:31.580 align:middle line:84%
because I had this mother who
was like you will not judge

00:04:31.580 --> 00:04:32.380 align:middle line:90%
others.

00:04:32.380 --> 00:04:35.080 align:middle line:84%
