will not have it--

00:04:35.080 --> 00:04:38.050 align:middle line:84%
while I was being
so severely judged.

00:04:38.050 --> 00:04:44.720 align:middle line:84%
And so what I sort of came to
know is that, in that learning,

00:04:44.720 --> 00:04:49.300 align:middle line:84%
I learned that the more I am
myself, the more that I am just

00:04:49.300 --> 00:04:54.280 align:middle line:84%
brazenly out there as
a metaphysical person,

00:04:54.280 --> 00:04:57.130 align:middle line:84%
a spiritual person, someone who
talks to angels, someone who

00:04:57.130 --> 00:04:59.860 align:middle line:84%
