someone who is also

00:04:59.860 --> 00:05:04.690 align:middle line:84%
gay and married to a
beautiful husband, and wears

00:05:04.690 --> 00:05:08.650 align:middle line:84%
sequins most of the time on
state and things like that,

00:05:08.650 --> 00:05:13.150 align:middle line:84%
the more I became myself
the more the world opened up

00:05:13.150 --> 00:05:14.023 align:middle line:90%
for me.

00:05:14.023 --> 00:05:15.190 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: That makes sense.

00:05:15.190 --> 00:05:16.648 align:middle line:84%
And you know,
Radleigh, most people

00:05:16.648 --> 00:05:18.280 align:middle line:90%
don't have that rough a path.

00:05:18.280 --> 00:05:20.540 align:middle line:84%
