significant parts of ourself.

00:05:34.580 --> 00:05:36.410 align:middle line:84%
And so I can see what
you're saying here.

00:05:36.410 --> 00:05:38.463 align:middle line:84%
This gift is what
do you have to lose.

00:05:38.463 --> 00:05:39.380 align:middle line:90%
>> VALENTINE: Nothing.

00:05:39.380 --> 00:05:41.180 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: I don't
have friends anyway.

00:05:41.180 --> 00:05:42.240 align:middle line:90%
