this mystical experience

00:05:47.690 --> 00:05:48.900 align:middle line:90%
after being a broadcaster.

00:05:48.900 --> 00:05:49.700 align:middle line:90%
Right.

00:05:49.700 --> 00:05:52.010 align:middle line:84%
Went on to TV and the
famous show in England,

00:05:52.010 --> 00:05:53.480 align:middle line:90%
