and stand up for who we are,

00:06:21.800 --> 00:06:23.832 align:middle line:84%
I think it would be a
more interesting planet.

00:06:23.832 --> 00:06:25.040 align:middle line:90%
>> VALENTINE: I think so too.

00:06:25.040 --> 00:06:27.560 align:middle line:84%
