00:06:45.740 --> 00:06:46.050 align:middle line:90%
>> VALENTINE: Yes.

00:06:46.050 --> 00:06:47.900 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: It breaks
down all the defenses.

00:06:47.900 --> 00:06:50.777 align:middle line:84%
