00:08:10.420 --> 00:08:11.510 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: But I like you.

00:08:11.510 --> 00:08:13.010 align:middle line:84%
>> VALENTINE: But then
he told everybody.

00:08:13.010 --> 00:08:13.400 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Oh yeah.

00:08:13.400 --> 00:08:14.070 align:middle line:90%
There you go.

00:08:14.070 --> 00:08:15.890 align:middle line:84%
>> VALENTINE: And so
because kids are kids.

00:08:15.890 --> 00:08:19.070 align:middle line:84%
